1
00:00:36,600 --> 00:00:37,160
It's her.

2
00:00:38,720 --> 00:00:40,850
She pushed Lapeng down from upstairs.

3
00:00:41,360 --> 00:00:42,840
I saw you two on the second floor

4
00:00:42,840 --> 00:00:44,300
having a fierce argument.

5
00:00:44,600 --> 00:00:46,000
Then you pushed him down.

6
00:00:46,240 --> 00:00:47,480
She is the murderer.

7
00:00:48,440 --> 00:00:48,960
Master.

8
00:00:49,480 --> 00:00:50,720
We can't let her go today.

9
00:00:50,720 --> 00:00:51,560
I did see him.

10
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:53,880
But I didn't do it.

11
00:01:02,400 --> 00:01:03,260
Master Angwei.

12
00:01:04,440 --> 00:01:05,700
Lapeng drank too much.

13
00:01:06,520 --> 00:01:07,380
He wanted to...

14
00:01:08,240 --> 00:01:08,920
to me...

15
00:01:12,600 --> 00:01:14,800
I didn't want to get tangled up with him.

16
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:16,640
He lost his footing and fell.

17
00:01:16,640 --> 00:01:17,700
I tried to grab him.

18
00:01:18,560 --> 00:01:19,680
But I couldn't.

19
00:01:22,120 --> 00:01:22,800
I'm a woman.

20
00:01:23,480 --> 00:01:23,960
How could I...

21
00:01:23,960 --> 00:01:24,420
Enough.

22
00:01:27,800 --> 00:01:28,260
Father.

23
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:32,300
Maybe it was just an accident.

24
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:33,729
An accident?

25
00:01:36,759 --> 00:01:39,080
I trained Lapeng myself.

26
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:41,440
I know his skills and personality

27
00:01:41,440 --> 00:01:42,640
better than anyone.

28
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:44,800
For him to just foolishly

29
00:01:44,800 --> 00:01:46,400
fall to his death like that,

30
00:01:46,960 --> 00:01:48,820
without even a chance to be saved.

31
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:49,720
No matter how you look at it,

32
00:01:49,720 --> 00:01:50,520
it's murder.

33
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:53,120
Yet you casually say

34
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:54,720
it's an accident.

35
00:01:56,360 --> 00:01:57,120
Angwei.

36
00:01:57,880 --> 00:02:00,480
Are you favoring this Miss Feifei?

37
00:02:02,880 --> 00:02:03,480
Father.

38
00:02:04,880 --> 00:02:06,680
Before the truth comes to light,

39
00:02:07,880 --> 00:02:10,139
I am willing to vouch for her with my life.

40
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:13,240
Ang Wei.

41
00:02:14,040 --> 00:02:15,970
No matter how you try to protect me,

42
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:19,520
I will make Sihai Group

43
00:02:20,640 --> 00:02:22,840
pay for what happened to the Dai family.

44
00:02:25,160 --> 00:02:25,680
Sir.

45
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:26,720
We can't let her go.

46
00:02:26,720 --> 00:02:27,720
Beat her to death.

47
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,400
This is a serious matter.

48
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:31,120
We absolutely cannot let her go today.

49
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:32,520
We must make her explain clearly

50
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:34,040
what her real purpose is.

51
00:02:34,480 --> 00:02:36,120
What if she wants to hurt us?

52
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:39,500
What if she wants to hurt the entire Sihai Group?

53
00:02:39,880 --> 00:02:40,400
Father,

54
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:45,600
we shouldn't easily trust people with ulterior motives.

55
00:02:57,480 --> 00:02:58,000
Sir,

56
00:02:58,160 --> 00:03:00,290
we can't let them just leave like this.

57
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:01,680
Sir.

58
00:03:04,720 --> 00:03:05,450
Uncle Danpa.

59
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:08,810
Ang Wei isn't the only one protecting Feifei.

60
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:10,490
She also has me, Ou Shaowen,

61
00:03:10,640 --> 00:03:12,100
and the entire Siam Group.

62
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:16,280
Shaowen, I won't see you out.

63
00:03:26,320 --> 00:03:27,880
Everyone, go back to work.

64
00:03:29,320 --> 00:03:29,920
Tell me,

65
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:32,120
did you plan Lapeng's death?

66
00:03:34,079 --> 00:03:34,560
I can

67
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:36,520
protect you in front of everyone,

68
00:03:36,760 --> 00:03:38,560
but that doesn't mean I'm a fool.

69
00:03:39,640 --> 00:03:40,960
You know Ruannila's weakness

70
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:42,000
inside out.

71
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:45,480
There's no way you knew nothing about Lapeng's alcohol tolerance.

72
00:03:45,480 --> 00:03:47,880
So you protected me in front of them earlier

73
00:03:48,920 --> 00:03:50,520
not because you believed me.

74
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:53,290
You were just saving your own face.

75
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:56,560
If that's the case, you can hand me over.

76
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:59,329
The innocent have nothing to hide.

77
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:01,200
You're quite the smooth talker.

78
00:04:02,440 --> 00:04:04,280
Earlier, I smelled

79
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:07,380
the same cologne on Ruannila and Lapeng.

80
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,120
This brand is rare.

81
00:04:09,880 --> 00:04:11,340
It can't be a coincidence.

82
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:13,480
What else do you know?

83
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:17,980
If Ruannila and Lapeng are having an affair,

84
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:19,760
then Ruannila

85
00:04:20,440 --> 00:04:22,040
also has a motive for murder.

86
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:26,600
Go on.

87
00:04:29,320 --> 00:04:30,450
I am your secretary.

88
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:33,159
I wanted to offer you a possibility.

89
00:04:33,760 --> 00:04:35,090
I completely trust you.

90
00:04:36,159 --> 00:04:37,080
But you didn't do that.

91
00:04:37,080 --> 00:04:39,210
Now you remember you're my secretary.

92
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:41,340
If you want me to trust you,

93
00:04:42,159 --> 00:04:43,960
keep your little tricks

94
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:44,920
and schemes to yourself.

95
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:46,180
Are you that innocent?

96
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:49,260
You trapped me with an agreement.

97
00:04:49,440 --> 00:04:50,700
Don't you have your own

98
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:52,980
ulterior motives?

99
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:08,680
You'd better stick with me for the next few days.

100
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:09,740
Don't go anywhere,

101
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:11,640
and don't talk to anyone.

102
00:05:11,960 --> 00:05:13,840
Otherwise, I can't guarantee that Sihai Group

103
00:05:13,840 --> 00:05:15,760
won't make you disappear.

104
00:05:19,840 --> 00:05:20,720
I work for you.

105
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:23,440
Naturally, I will listen to you.

106
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:28,960
Master.

107
00:05:29,440 --> 00:05:31,520
Lapeng was your capable subordinate.

108
00:05:31,520 --> 00:05:33,600
As soon as this mysterious Feifei arrived,

109
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:34,400
he died.

110
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:36,680
Look at the dress she's wearing today.

111
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:39,400
It's exactly the same as the one Dailing used to like.

112
00:05:39,400 --> 00:05:42,000
She's just pretending to be a ghost to scare us.

113
00:05:42,760 --> 00:05:44,640
Ghosts are easier to deal with than the living.

114
00:05:44,640 --> 00:05:46,040
Even if Dailing were here,

115
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:47,120
so what?

116
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:48,840
Besides,

117
00:05:49,520 --> 00:05:50,720
Lapeng's death

118
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:54,000
isn't necessarily a bad thing.

119
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,680
Taking the secret to his grave

120
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:58,560
is a fitting end for him.

121
00:06:00,960 --> 00:06:02,800
What if she really is Dailing?

122
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:07,600
Oh, Ruan Nila,

123
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:09,680
you're really embarrassing me.

124
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:12,480
Getting so scared of a little girl.

125
00:06:13,960 --> 00:06:15,420
If you are really worried,

126
00:06:15,640 --> 00:06:16,960
send two capable subordinates

127
00:06:16,960 --> 00:06:18,360
to check her background.

128
00:06:18,640 --> 00:06:19,880
But keep it quiet.

129
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:23,040
If people find out,

130
00:06:23,400 --> 00:06:25,200
they'll laugh at our Sihai Group

131
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:27,010
for bullying a little girl.

132
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:29,060
What about Ang Wei?

133
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:32,200
Could he have known she was Dai Ling long ago

134
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:33,690
and conspired with her?

135
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:36,040
Are we the next ones to be dealt with?

136
00:06:36,640 --> 00:06:37,600
Many years ago,

137
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:40,159
Dai Ling died by his hands.

138
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:41,360
Perhaps

139
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:44,480
he is the one who least wants

140
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,930
this girl to be Dai Ling.

141
00:06:46,159 --> 00:06:47,890
He's just finding a substitute

142
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:50,360
to ease his guilt.

143
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:52,400
When the initial excitement

144
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:53,440
fades away,

145
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:55,960
he will naturally know where to stand

146
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:57,159
and what to do.

147
00:06:58,480 --> 00:06:59,210
Don't worry.

148
00:07:28,400 --> 00:07:29,000
Hurry.

149
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:44,490
Why was there so much noise in the room?

150
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:46,380
What are you doing in here?

151
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:47,560
What noise?

152
00:07:48,840 --> 00:07:49,920
Mr. Ang Wei,

153
00:07:50,400 --> 00:07:51,930
you're being too paranoid.

154
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:57,920
You're lying.

155
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:01,440
There's someone else's scent in this room.

156
00:08:03,960 --> 00:08:04,960
Mr. Ang Wei,

157
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:08,060
are you suspecting me of hiding a man?

158
00:08:09,320 --> 00:08:10,400
I didn't say that.

159
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:14,920
But you act like it.

160
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:19,570
What if there's someone

161
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:23,000
who wants to harm you hiding in the room?

162
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:26,300
What would you do then?

163
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:28,600
Besides,

164
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:34,240
besides,

165
00:08:35,559 --> 00:08:37,360
Ruannila wants you dead now.

166
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:42,440
It never hurts to be careful.

167
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:44,240
Are you worried about me?

168
00:08:51,680 --> 00:08:53,920
I'm just afraid you'll die in my room.

169
00:08:56,680 --> 00:08:57,940
That would be bad luck.

170
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:04,520
I wonder how Sister Hua is doing.

171
00:09:05,040 --> 00:09:06,440
I need to get him to leave.

172
00:09:11,920 --> 00:09:13,920
Are you really not worried about me?

173
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:19,610
Miss Feifei, you're being too presumptuous.

174
00:09:22,880 --> 00:09:23,960
In that case,

175
00:09:25,160 --> 00:09:26,160
please go back.

176
00:09:27,240 --> 00:09:29,440
After all, I'm your private secretary,

177
00:09:29,560 --> 00:09:30,560
not your lover.

178
00:09:32,760 --> 00:09:34,160
Being alone late at night

179
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:36,080
will cause gossip.

180
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:39,890
It's not peaceful in Sihai lately.

181
00:09:40,520 --> 00:09:41,720
Stay safe.

182
00:09:43,240 --> 00:09:44,600
If some shady person

183
00:09:44,600 --> 00:09:45,760
enters your room,

184
00:09:46,560 --> 00:09:47,690
remember to tell me.

185
00:10:01,920 --> 00:10:03,160
The assassin just now,

186
00:10:03,160 --> 00:10:05,090
I'm sure it was Ruannila's person.

187
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:07,700
Without Danpa's tacit approval,

188
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:09,520
Ruannila wouldn't dare kill me,

189
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:12,160
especially on Ang Wei's turf.

190
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:15,440
Lapeng just died,

191
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:17,820
and they can't sit still anymore.

192
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,500
Even if it's not Danpa,

193
00:10:19,920 --> 00:10:21,450
he's happy to see it happen.

194
00:10:21,800 --> 00:10:23,480
Ruannila will take the blame afterwards,

195
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:24,680
and he will reap the benefits.

196
00:10:24,680 --> 00:10:26,000
They are in cahoots.

197
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:30,360
So we need to figure out a way

198
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:33,000
to make them turn on each other.
